\sum_{k=0}^{n} \frac{k}{n^2+k^2}
\lim_{n \to \infty} \sum_{k=0}^n \dfrac{k}{n^2 + k^2} =    \lim_{n \to \infty} \sum_{k=0}^n \dfrac{1}{n} \dfrac{\dfrac{k}{n}}{1 + \left(\dfrac{k}{n}\right)^2}.
